    "title": "Assistant Store Manager - HomeTown - Apply Now",
    "description": "We at HomeTown are looking for an experienced Assistant Store Manager based out of Vadodara. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout HomeTown:\nHomeTown is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with HomeTown!",
